Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.73,0:00:13.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}アリと何ひとつ変わらない いや　それ以上に…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.73,0:00:13.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That two billion reward \Nper spider is attractive, but finding them will be impossible. Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.33,0:02:00.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}運悪く爆死を免れた者の体内に 効率良く取り込まれ 迅速に内部を破壊すると同時に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.33,0:02:00.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Very x Sharp x Eye
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.24,0:02:04.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}被毒者の肉体が 毒そのものとなり
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.24,0:02:04.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Gon and his friends are \Npursuing the Phantom Troupe, and have now obtained the money
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.23,0:02:08.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}新たな毒を放出しながら やがて　死に至る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.23,0:02:08.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}to buy the information they need.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.77,0:02:13.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その毒の量と死ぬまでの時間が 実に絶妙で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.77,0:02:13.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's crazy... You actually have money.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.74,0:02:18.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}大量の連鎖被毒者を 生み出せる点にあった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.74,0:02:18.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Man, you really pawned \Nyour Hunter License?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:20.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}要するに…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:20.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You're insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.25,0:02:22.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.25,0:02:22.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So, what should we do first?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.74,0:02:28.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.74,0:02:28.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Let's start by purchasing \Na Southernbees catalog.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.77,0:02:34.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}この上なく非人道的な 悪魔兵器だったのである
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.77,0:02:34.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Here is this year's \NSouthernbees auction catalog.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.23,0:04:12.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}こ…　これは…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.23,0:04:12.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Remember how four-eyes mentioned that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:17.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私の身に　一体　何が？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:17.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}really talented people use Nen without \Neven realizing it themselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.23,0:04:24.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}プフ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.23,0:04:24.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Wing-san. He taught us Nen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:33.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いかがされました？　メルエム様。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:33.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If we search for items with \Naura on them, like this knife, it's likely some genius made them. I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.78,0:04:42.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もしや 考え直していただけましたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.78,0:04:42.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}with no formal appraisal training. Then we auction the items at a higher price!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.71,0:04:46.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それならば　一刻も早く避難を。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.71,0:04:46.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you guys want that, \Nwrite down your price.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:50.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:50.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Customers are supposed to \Nname their own prices?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:53.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}見え透いていてもなお
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:53.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah, that's how this market works.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.21,0:05:05.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}決して自らは言わぬか まぁ　よい。 余が先に　残りの侵入者を 捕獲すれば済む話。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.21,0:05:05.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You write down what you're willing to pay, and when time expires, \Nthe highest bidder wins the item. Understand? Popular items
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:09.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お主の秘密 がぜん　興味が湧いて来た。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:09.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}will see their prices shoot up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.71,0:05:15.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}洗いざらい話す旨　まさか ほごにする気はあるまいな？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.71,0:05:15.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.22,0:05:23.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}この身　ちぎれても 約束は守りまする。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.22,0:05:23.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll check the online forums. Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:29.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}よかろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:29.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This is a weird pot, but I detect aura...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:45.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あと１回だけという 約束の「円」を　もう？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:45.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Even if you end up bidding too high, \Nyou'll succeed in discouraging any rivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.21,0:05:49.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}見える
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.21,0:05:49.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}500 multiplied by 2.5...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:51.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}全て
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:51.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:06:00.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}前には　なかった足跡が
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:06:00.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's the same person!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.24,0:06:04.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}乗り捨てられた車が
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.24,0:06:04.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Same on your side?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:07.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ユピーの骸が
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:07.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I found a couple items, but both had bids already placed by "Zepile."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:15.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}閉まっていた扉が 新たに 余の「円」に反応した者も
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:15.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And after I entered a bid 2.5 times higher, he multiplied that by 4. Then it isn't a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:20.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ん!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:20.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What should we do? Keep placing bids until the deadline.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.78,0:06:25.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なっ…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.78,0:06:25.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There are two of us, so we'll win some!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:34.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ユピーを仕留めたのは貴様か？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:34.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So ultimately, we won three and lost one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:39.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}と…　とんでもございません！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:39.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah, he got that weird pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:41.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なぜ　師団長の私めが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:41.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Well, that wasn't too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.22,0:06:44.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ユピー殿を　あやめる道理など ございましょうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.22,0:06:44.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Let's take these to the auction house now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.29,0:06:48.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ユピー殿は
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.29,0:06:48.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I am very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.32,0:06:57.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私めと話をしている最中に 突然　吐血し　苦しみだし 果てたのでございます！ 誓って　うそではございません！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.32,0:06:57.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But the auction house cannot \Naccept any additional items, once the catalog has been published. Isn't there any way?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:07:03.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これは　うそじゃ　ねえ！ 俺は… 俺は　確かにユピーを撃った
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:07:03.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We really want to auction these.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.76,0:07:07.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.76,0:07:07.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I suggest that you give \Nthe trade market a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:11.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}奴は俺の質問に答える前に…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:11.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The trade market?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:17.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺の「クロムカデ」がかえる前に 苦しみだし くたばった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:17.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The trade market... Professionals will be here, so if one of these \Nis genuine, we should get a great price.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:21.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}恐らく　私めと会う前に
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:21.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I wanted to sell these at the auction, though. How much do you think we'll get?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:25.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}すでに何らかの敵の攻撃を 受けていたのでございます！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:25.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Let's find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:33.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}よって　私めは　賊が群衆に 紛れていないかを調べるため ここに来た次第でございます！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:33.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Oh, you found these in your cellar? Yep! Dad said to sell them if the price was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:37.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:37.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}These are wonderful pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.71,0:07:42.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クッ…　護衛軍プフ 厄介な奴が来やがった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.71,0:07:42.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Only fifty copies were printed, and yours has a single-digit serial number.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:47.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}こいつには何か こっちの心を見透かす力がある
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:47.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And an authentic autograph. We know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:53.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}この場で何を言いだすか 分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:53.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'd guess it's worth at least 150,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:56.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}きゃつは　口止めでは　ぬるい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:56.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This antique doll is also excellent...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:08:03.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}できれば 今すぐにでも始末すべき 強引に　叛意ありと断罪し 処分する
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:08:03.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's in great shape, and the pristine condition of both \Nbox and doll raises the value.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.72,0:08:07.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}最悪でも　王から引き離さねば
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.72,0:08:07.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm estimating 300,000. However, this one isn't worth much, unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:11.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}メルエム様　そ奴は…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:11.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:19.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「円」で触れた者の感情を 読み取れるようになった。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:19.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The box was made recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:23.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}こ奴の余へ向けられた ただならぬ敵意もな。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:23.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The statue is rough and doesn't \Nadhere to any theme. I'd say it's only worth 1,500 Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:28.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}な…　なんと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:28.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But there is a little aura...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:33.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}一度　余の 「円」にさらされた者の心は
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:33.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}However, that would be its \Nappraisal as an artwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.21,0:08:36.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}目を凝らすだけで　よく見えるわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.21,0:08:36.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The wood itself is quite valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:40.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ユピーの翼や砲撃のみならず
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:40.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So I'll make you an offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:43.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私の 「スピリチュアルメッセージ」も
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:43.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you sell me the painting \Nand doll for 420,000, I'll buy the wood for 80,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.74,0:08:49.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}より高い次元の能力として 見事に昇華されている
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.74,0:08:49.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A total of 500,000? What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:51.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:51.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Feel free to think it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:56.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王！ 王は無敵！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:56.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But I doubt anyone will quote \Nyou a better price.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:09:01.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王は無二！ なのに…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:09:01.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In the meantime, let me \Ncheck this wood's age. Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:05.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なぜに！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:05.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Put down that statue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:17.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}言いようのない不安が 満たされて行くのでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:17.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He's offering a fair price \Nfor the painting and doll, but he's lying about the statue! I-I never lied!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.23,0:09:29.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}波のように寄せる 余への強い殺意は隠しようもない。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.23,0:09:29.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No collector would pay \N80,000 for that wood. You're interested in the contents of that statue!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.21,0:09:46.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}申してみよ　偽りは許さぬ。 うっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.21,0:09:46.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's a wooden trove. A wooden trove? Three hundred years ago, these were a popular way for the \Nwealthy to hide their money.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:49.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}感情に流されている 場合ではない！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:49.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}To hide their money...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:52.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ありのままを。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:52.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If it's real, there should be valuables inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.21,0:09:56.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}メルエム様！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.21,0:09:56.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You planned to steal the contents, \Nwhile pretending to check its age!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:10:01.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}手順違いにございます。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:10:01.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I-I would never do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:20.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その者は 私の秘密に深くかかわる者。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:20.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But that only tells us the material's age. The statue itself could be modern.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:22.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}しかし　それを自覚せぬ者。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:22.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This technique is known as hoodwinking, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.71,0:10:25.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ん!?　ん!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.71,0:10:25.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Technique?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:32.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}図らずも　その者の口から 私の秘め事の一部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:32.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He's referring to a counterfeiter trying \Nto trick a professional appraiser. But that isn't what I'm doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.32,0:10:36.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もしくは全てが漏れることも 十分あり得まする。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.32,0:10:36.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Here's a seam that an amateur would never recognize. The seam contains an adhesive
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:39.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王の能力を前にして
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:39.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}used back in that period.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.21,0:10:43.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うそは無力　ならば真実で！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.21,0:10:43.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You're insisting this is a real wooden trove?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:50.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}勝敗を決する前に 戦利品の中身を知るは 王の本意と真逆でございましょう。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:50.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah. But it is possible that it was opened \Nonce to swap out its contents, and the statue was reassembled.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:54.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}真実のみで ごまかしてみせる！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:54.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We'd call that a dud.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.31,0:11:03.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私との勝負 継続を　お望みならば その者との質疑 何とぞ　後回しにされますよう。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.31,0:11:03.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's called double-dipping, placing new adhesive on top \Nof the old to create a dud.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.73,0:11:07.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}こいつは一体 何　言ってやがる？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.73,0:11:07.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But only an amateur would try that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:10.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}秘密…　何のことだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:10.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A professional would melt \Nthe adhesive with a flame, before resealing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:15.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いや　それよりも この場をどうする？ どうすれば　逃げ切れる？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:15.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That way, it would appear as though \Nthe statue had never been opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.78,0:11:18.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}この怪物から！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.78,0:11:18.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's known as welding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.21,0:11:24.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}チクショ　まさか　こんな ばかげた化け物だとは！ さっさと逃げりゃ よかったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.21,0:11:24.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It hasn't been welded. If fire were used, the wood would be scarred \Nor the adhesive would have discolored.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:27.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}魔が差したんだ　クソ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:27.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Even the pros have a hard time \Nweighing those details.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:31.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}目の前で あんなに強大だったユピーが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:31.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can't trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:35.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ちっぽけな虫くずみてぇに あっさり　くたばりやがるから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:35.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm a pro appraiser! I swear by my eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.28,0:11:37.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何か　俺でも王を やれるんじゃねえかみてぇに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.28,0:11:37.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This is a real wooden trove!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:43.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}錯覚しちまった 残っちまった 酔っちまったんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:43.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's never been opened, and the treasure inside \Nhasn't been swapped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.21,0:11:58.20,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そうだ　バカだ俺は！ 酔ってたんだ俺は！ いろいろ一遍に起きて ジャイロのこと思い出して
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.21,0:11:58.20,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Okay, let's assume that this is a \Ngenuine wooden trove. If the contents have been swapped out, what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.20,0:12:06.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}パニクって　センチになって ヒロイズムに酔っちまったんだ！ ジャイロのあだ討ちみてぇな 気分になって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.20,0:12:06.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll be your slave for the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:13.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ジャイロは死んじゃいねえのに きっと生きてるのに こっから逃げて また一緒につるんで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:13.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.23,0:12:27.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}感情を狂わせやがった 俺のレールを 変えやがったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.23,0:12:27.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Wow! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:32.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クソったれ 何がメッセンジャーだ！ 何とかしねえと…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:32.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Oh, so you're Zepile.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:36.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺の敵意もバレてる うそは通用しねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:36.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Thanks, Zepile-san. You don't need to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.28,0:12:41.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「ミサイルマン」は発動させる前に 俺の首が消し飛ぶだろう！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.28,0:12:41.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Consider it give and take. Twenty percent sounds fair. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.23,0:12:45.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何が残ってる？　俺の手駒に
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.23,0:12:45.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}My cut when you sell the treasure. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.22,0:12:48.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}メッセージ？　プフの秘密？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.22,0:12:48.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You're going to rob us?! That's uncalled for.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:50.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺の感情の根源？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:50.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's my fee for providing advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:53.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これを総動員して　俺は…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:53.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I don't see a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:56.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}一体　助かるのか？ 何を言えば？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:56.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He helped us back there. Now, look here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.76,0:13:02.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}最初の… 初めの　ひと言が勝負だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.76,0:13:02.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We need to collect as much \NJenny as we possibly can. I might be willing to buy him lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.24,0:13:06.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}生死を分かつ 一世一代のひと言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.24,0:13:06.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Really? Then I'll settle for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:11.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}間違えたら　その瞬間 全部　終わるかもしれねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:11.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Huh? So, Zepile-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:25.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}プフ　その秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:25.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In return, just tell me something. What tipped you off to bid on these items?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:30.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そ奴が余に向ける憎悪と わずかでも…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:30.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Is it okay to tell him the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.72,0:13:38.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}かかわりがあると申すか？ これが王…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.72,0:13:38.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Well, it beats paying him. I see, Nen aura...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:47.20,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}余を遮り　言葉尻を捉えた揚げ句 指図まがいの進言。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:47.20,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you're telling the truth, that explains why you bought the statue, not realizing something was hidden inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:50.70,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}よほどの覚悟の上であろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:50.70,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So, why do you need money so badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:55.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}心して答えよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:55.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We can answer that question, \Nbut not for free. Afterwards, you have to answer our question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.24,0:13:56.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これは…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.24,0:13:56.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Sure, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:14:03.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王の新たな能力は プフの返答を待つまでもなく
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:14:03.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There's an item we want \Nto buy at the auction. That's why we need money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:06.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}是非の判定を可能としている
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:06.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Oh, which item are you interested in? It's our turn now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:10.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}プフの 絶対的心服を知りつつなお
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:10.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You estimated that this treasure \Nwas worth 300 million, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:15.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まがまがしく明瞭に発せられる 殺意にまみれたオーラは
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:15.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Could we receive that much \Nat the trade market?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:20.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}是非にかかわらず　その答えが 王の意にそぐわぬ場合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:20.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}At the trade market? They mainly deal in hard cash...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:25.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}死をもって償う他ないことを 示していた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:25.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you show up abruptly, \Nyou won't get a fair price. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.72,0:14:29.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}忠義も　敵意も
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.72,0:14:29.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Seriously? Now it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.21,0:14:33.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王の前では　皆　平等に無価値
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.21,0:14:33.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll repeat the question. Which item do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.71,0:14:36.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}誰も止められない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.71,0:14:36.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A game called Greed Island. Oh, that ridiculously expensive game?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:43.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私は
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:43.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}How much is that weird pot \Nthat you bought worth?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:46.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あの時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:46.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Huh? This? It's garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.72,0:14:50.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}すでに死を覚悟した身
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.72,0:14:50.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.73,0:14:54.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}殉じよう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.73,0:14:54.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why do you want that expensive game? I believe it costs 6 billion?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.72,0:14:59.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}己の忠義に
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.72,0:14:59.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The asking price is 8.9 billion. We're looking for his dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:05.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何も申し上げるわけには まいりません。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:05.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That game has a clue inside. Oh... Why did you choose that pot?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.73,0:15:10.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}勝負の途中　故。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.73,0:15:10.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you knew the wooden trove was real, shouldn't you have bid on \Nthe more valuable item?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.73,0:15:17.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ただ　それだけのこと
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.73,0:15:17.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But you went for the pot. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:31.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}常軌を逸する決意　狂気が…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:31.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But it wasn't an original creation. It was a replica. In other words, a counterfeit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:37.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王を止めた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:37.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Once I became an appraiser \Nand began earning money, I quit doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.73,0:15:53.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}腹が　へったな。 しかし…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.73,0:15:53.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When I see how poorly these are made, I feel mortified! So I browse the markets and buy them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.71,0:15:56.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ヒィ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.71,0:15:56.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}How much would a real one cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.21,0:15:59.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ウェルフィンは 即座に理解した
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.21,0:15:59.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's my turn. What does your dad do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.71,0:16:01.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺は…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.71,0:16:01.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He's a pro Hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:06.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺は食われて死ぬ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:06.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}How much would a real one cost?! Forty to fifty thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.22,0:16:13.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}およそ１秒先
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.22,0:16:13.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There are a few in the antiques world, and not one of them is ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.71,0:16:19.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}死ぬ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.71,0:16:19.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Won't it be impossible for you \Ntwo to find him alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.72,0:16:24.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}自身の未来を知った ウェルフィンの風貌は
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.72,0:16:24.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It'll be fine. \NI'm a pro Hunter, too. Huh? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.24,0:16:29.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}一瞬にして　１００年余りが 過ぎたかのごとく変わり果てた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.24,0:16:29.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Okay, your turn to ask a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.73,0:16:31.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}生きたい！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.73,0:16:31.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Okay, this is my final question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.21,0:16:40.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その間　脳裏では 過去の一切が高速で雑然と流れ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.21,0:16:40.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Can I help you with anything? Huh? If you want to make money at an auction, \Nyou'll need an appraiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.74,0:16:49.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その直後　はじけ散り 現在と混ざり合った ひと言！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.74,0:16:49.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You could even say that with an appraiser, you can always turn a profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:52.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}最初の！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:52.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You can set the price you want to pay me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.21,0:16:54.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}最期の！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.21,0:16:54.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.23,0:16:59.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}生への執着と 不可避の死との境界で
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.23,0:16:59.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then you have to answer our last question.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.22,0:17:05.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ひと言　メッセージ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.22,0:17:05.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why do you want to help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:08.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王との　ひと言！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:08.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Because it made me happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:13.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あの時　プフがピトーと ひと言！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:13.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It made me happy that this piece of junk actually caught your eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:16.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}プフの秘密　ひと言！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:16.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's not a piece of junk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.71,0:17:19.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺は　ひと言
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.71,0:17:19.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It definitely holds your Nen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.71,0:17:22.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}死ぬまでは死なねえ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.71,0:17:22.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Everyone has some aura...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:29.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}かつてなく　目まぐるしく働いた 脳細胞が導き出したのは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:29.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But it's incredibly difficult to harness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.22,0:17:33.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}通常であれば 選択し得ないものだった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.22,0:17:33.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You must concentrate and \Ntrain for a very long time. I can tell how much effort you \Nput into making that pot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:43.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}コムギ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:43.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I still think it's a weird pot, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.21,0:18:49.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}こ…　これほどとは…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.21,0:18:49.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That isn't important at all! But they sound fun! \NLike magic tricks! We're not here to have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:04.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}プフ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:04.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When I admitted to making forgeries
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.73,0:19:10.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これが　其のほうの…。 はい。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.73,0:19:10.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}and when that trader gave me a hard time... He didn't react with accusatory glares
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:18.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何なりと処罰を。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:18.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}or by plotting his own evil deeds. His reaction was very simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:30.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}我らは異体同心　とがなどない。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:30.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Which means that he's dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.22,0:19:34.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}かなうはずなどない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.22,0:19:34.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Someone who can never truly be appraised.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.75,0:19:43.70,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}引き続き　ピトーを捜せ。 捕らえた２名が 何か知っているかもしれぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.75,0:19:43.70,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Welding is the hardest \Ntechnique to see through.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:49.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}聞き出せたら解放してやれ。 そ奴らに聞きたいことは もう　ない。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:49.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But recently, a new technique has surfaced. It's known as exposing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:55.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うなずく他　あろうはずもない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:55.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You plainly reveal the opened statue
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:57.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}はっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:57.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}along with a fake treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.72,0:20:06.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}開いた扉　奥へ続く足跡 「円」で触れた２名の覚悟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.72,0:20:06.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Because people assume that you wouldn't open the statue \Nif the treasure were fake, you can fool them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.73,0:20:10.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}全てが一つの解を指している
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.73,0:20:10.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But now this technique is getting old.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:12.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ウェルフィン。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:12.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When people started to get suspicious, \Na new technique emerged.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:18.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}はっ！　はい！ コムギは 地下格納庫のどこかに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:18.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Can you guess what it is? I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:20.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}女とタコと共にいる。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:20.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The treasure inside is also fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.79,0:20:24.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お主は　それを 余か護衛軍に知らせる役目。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.79,0:20:24.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Wrong! I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.73,0:20:26.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}な…　なぜ　それを！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.73,0:20:26.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Remove the treasure from a different place!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.73,0:20:30.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お主が役目を引き受けた 理由のカギは
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.73,0:20:30.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.22,0:20:36.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}タコにありそうだが 役目を全うしなかった理由は また　別。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.22,0:20:36.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You can create a new opening \Nand remove the treasure, then insert the fake \Ntreasure and seal the hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.72,0:20:41.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それは　余への憎悪の根源に 起因するか？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.72,0:20:41.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This is known as side-stepping. Side-stepping...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.81,0:20:44.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}図星か。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.81,0:20:44.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Many veteran appraisers have been fooled.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.73,0:20:51.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}安心せい。 答えた後は　どこへ行こうと お主の自由だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.73,0:20:51.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They assume the statue is real if the \Nadhesive hasn't changed color from the application of fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:54.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}礼を言う。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:54.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's how they fool the pros.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.72,0:20:59.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お主のおかげで 大切なものを思い出せた。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.72,0:20:59.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You live in an incredible world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.24,0:21:00.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うぅ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.24,0:21:00.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:07.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}奴らは Ｄエリアのビゼフ私庭で待つと。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:07.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What? A spider? Yeah, this looks real. There's a video attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.22,0:21:13.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うぅ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.22,0:21:13.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A man and a woman. I'll leave now, so let's meet there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:19.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}貴様は　貴様らは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:19.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Let's go, Killua. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:23.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}敵だ！　俺達の！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:23.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hey! What about the auction?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.72,0:21:26.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}さようか。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.72,0:21:26.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We'll let you handle it! Try to get us a good price!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.71,0:21:29.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハァ　ハァ　ハァ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.71,0:21:29.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.71,0:21:37.20,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}会えるといいな　その者と。 そして　可能なら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.71,0:21:37.20,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Okay! I've got it covered!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.20,0:21:43.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}人として生きるがよい。 うっ　うぅ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.20,0:21:43.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Gon and Killua have learned \Nabout a whole new world.
